title: Georginio Wijnaldum's four goals give Newcastle vital Premier League... - Theboltonnews.co.uk
text:
Georginio Wijnaldum hit Norwich for four as Newcastle finally ended their wait for a Barclays Premier League victory at the ninth attempt. The Dutchman scored twice before the break and added two more as the Magpies survived a major test of their resolve to survive a concerted fightback by the visitors before running out 6-2 winners.
 Theboltonnews.co.uk.
